value.text: I relied on three other methods to keep my pubescent concubine in submission
I had some experience in my life of pederosis

Between the age limits of nine and fourteen there occur maidens [...] and those creatures I propose to designate as "nymphets".
Lolita, light of my life, fire of my loins.
And this is the only immortality you and I may share, my Lolita
